# Umbilical cord tomb of Taejo of Joseon Dynasty

| region         = Geumsan County
}}
The Umbilical cord tomb of Taejo of Joseon Dynasty () is a tomb in Geumsan, South Korea, where the umbilical cords of Taejo of Joseon and his son JeongJong are buried.
It was originally located in Ryongyon County, and was moved to its current location in 1393.
